#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Handle all your customers in a breeze and get a nice overview of your income"
" through the reporting features that are integrated in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Administrér alle dine kunder nemt, og få et klart overblik over din "
"omsætning med Odoos integrerede rapportfunktioner."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If applicable, you can invoice your presence to your customer through the "
"invoice app. You can configure your invoice templates to include terms &amp;"
" conditions, as well as other handy features."
msgstr ""
"Har du behov for det, kan du fakturere dine timer til kunderne med "
"faktureringsappen. Du kan tilpasse fakturaformularerne med dine generelle "
"forretningsbetingelser og drage fordel af en række andre nyttige funktioner."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If applicable, you can of course directly manage your events directly in the"
" Field service app without going through the CRM and Sales app."
msgstr ""
"Om nødvendigt kan du også administrere dine arrangementer direkte i appen "
"for Udkørende Service helt uden at bruge CRM- eller Salgsappen."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to easily discover every features of this package, try "
"downloading the Demo Data."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du blot vil udforske alle funktionerne i denne pakke, kan du downloade "
"demodataene."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In some cases, you will get bookings from customers (coporate, etc.) for you"
" to attend an company event or other similar events."
msgstr ""
"I nogle tilfælde kan du modtage bookinger fra kunder, f.eks. virksomheder, "
"der ønsker, at du deltager i firmaarrangementer eller lignende events."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Incoming opportunities can be registered into your CRM. Manage opportunity "
"stages in the kanban view, categorization using tags, to-do's and reminders "
"using activities, and communication through the chatter."
msgstr ""
"Indgående salgsmuligheder kan registreres i dit CRM-system. Hold styr på "
"faserne i Kanban-visningen, kategoriser dem med tags, opret opgaver og "
"påmindelser via aktiviteter, og kommunikér direkte gennem chatteren."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Install the <strong>Social Marketing App </strong>to manage your social "
"media presence."
msgstr ""
"Installér appen til <strong>Markedsføring på sociale medier </strong>for at "
"styrke din tilstedeværelse på sociale medier."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Invoice your customers using the <strong>Invoice app</strong>"
msgstr "Fakturér dine kunder via <strong>Faktureringsappen</strong>"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Invoicing Documentation"
msgstr "Dokumentation til Fakturering"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Just be careful, once demo data are uploaded, it cannot be easily deleted. "
"But you can restart a fresh database on"
msgstr ""
"Bemærk: Når demodata er uploadet, kan de ikke slettes. Du kan dog oprette en "
"ny database på"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Manage your <strong>Purchases and Inventory</strong> in Odoo as well."
msgstr "Administrér også <strong>Indkøb og lagerprocesser</strong> i Odoo."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your presence at events using the <strong>Field Service app</strong>"
msgstr ""
"Hold styr på din deltagelse ved arrangementer med appen til "
"<strong>Udkørende Service</strong>"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model:crm.tag,name:food_trucks.crm_tag_7
msgid "Multi-Day"
msgstr "Flere dage"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Need a Website? No problem, Odoo can do it as well."
msgstr "Har du brug for en hjemmeside? Intet problem, det klarer Odoo for dig."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo.com/trial"
msgstr "Odoo.com/trial"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once you have all the information regarding this opportunity, you can make a"
" new quotation. Define how long you'll be staying, and if relevant, other "
"things you will be charging to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Når du har modtaget alle oplysninger om salgsmuligheden, kan du oprette et "
"nyt tilbud. Angiv, hvor længe du bliver, og beregn eventuelle øvrige "
"udgifter for kunden."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Point of Sale Documentation"
msgstr "Dokumentation til POS"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Reach us"
msgstr "Kontakt os"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Sales Documentation"
msgstr "Dokumentation til Salg"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Send quotations to prospective customers through the <strong>Sales "
"app</strong>"
msgstr "Send tilbud til potentielle kunder med <strong>Salgsappen</strong>"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Take a look at the <strong>Email Marketing App</strong> to let past "
"customers know what you're up to !"
msgstr ""
"Brug <strong>appen til e-mailmarketing</strong> til at informere tidligere "
"kunder om, hvad der sker hos dig!"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "Use the <strong>CRM app</strong> to manage your opportunities"
msgstr "Brug <strong>CRM-appen</strong> til at håndtere salgsmuligheder"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When your prospective customer confirms the sale, a new task is created in your field service app, and linked back to your sale order. You can manage assignations, needs, and so on from there and obtain a handy overview of your\n"
"        planning."
msgstr ""
"Når din potentielle kunde bekræfter salget, oprettes automatisk en ny opgave "
"i Salgsappen, knyttet til salgsordren. Herfra kan du administrere "
"tildelinger, forespørgsler og få et klart overblik over din\n"
"        planlægning."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"While on the field, you can take orders and payments from your customers or from the attendees through the Point of Sale app. The app is a fully featured point-of-sale solution that supports menus, products, quantities, discounts,\n"
"        pricelists, custom notes, and many other features."
msgstr ""
"Når du er på arbejde, kan du modtage ordrer fra kunder samt registrere "
"bestillinger og betalinger i POS-appen. Appen tilbyder funktioner til "
"menukort, produkter, mængder, rabatter,\n"
"        prislister, individuelle noter og meget mere."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With the Food Trucks Industry Package, you have all you need to manage your "
"business from customer bookings to invoicing, including a point-of-sale "
"system and much more."
msgstr ""
"Med Foodtruck-pakken kan du administrere hele din virksomhed fra "
"kundebestillinger til fakturering, inklusive kassesystem og meget mere."

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or explore more features?"
msgstr ""
"Vil du gerne tale med os om dit Odoo-setup eller udforske flere funktioner?"

#. module: food_trucks
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_trucks.welcome_article_body
msgid "You can still do it by upgrading your package in Apps."
msgstr "Du kan fortsat gøre dette ved at opdatere din pakke via Apps."

